<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>My Blog</title>
  <meta name="description" content="A simple personal blog created with HTML and TailwindCSS">
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-900">

  <!-- Navbar -->
  <header class="bg-white shadow sticky top-0 z-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">My Blog</h1>
      <nav>
        <a href="index.html" class="px-3 hover:text-blue-600">Home</a>
        <a href="#about" class="px-3 hover:text-blue-600">About</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-blue-600 text-white py-20 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold">Welcome to My Blog</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-lg">Sharing thoughts, tutorials, and ideas</p>
  </section>

  <!-- Blog Posts -->
  <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">

    <!-- Post 1 -->
    <article class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow hover:shadow-lg transition">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-600 mb-2">Getting Started with Blogging</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Blogging is one of the best ways to share your knowledge, ideas, and experiences with the world. In this post, we'll explore how to start your own blog easily...</p>
      <a href="post1.html" class="text-blue-600 font-medium hover:underline">Read More →</a>
    </article>

    <!-- Post 2 -->
    <article class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow hover:shadow-lg transition">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-600 mb-2">Why Consistency Matters</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Consistency is the key to growing an audience. Whether it's writing daily, weekly, or monthly, having a regular schedule builds trust with readers...</p>
      <a href="post2.html" class="text-blue-600 font-medium hover:underline">Read More →</a>
    </article>

  </main>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-white py-6 text-center mt-10">
    <p>© 2025 My Blog | Made with ❤️ using HTML & TailwindCSS</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
